        <h3 class="changelog-title">Dark Mode &amp; UX Polish</h3>
        <ul class="changelog-items">
          <li><strong>Dark Mode</strong> &mdash; Appearance toggle (Light / Dark / System) in Settings, saved across launches. All views render correctly in both modes.</li>
          <li><strong>Richer History</strong> &mdash; Tap any transcription to see the full text, WPM speed, and duration. Average WPM now shown on Dashboard. WPM shown inline on each history row.</li>
          <li><strong>Recording Quality</strong> &mdash; 300 ms grace delay before stopping so the last word is never cut off.</li>
          <li><strong>Settings Cleanup</strong> &mdash; Microphone permissions surfaced at the top, redundant Formality setting removed.</li>
          <li><strong>Bug Fixes</strong> &mdash; Window remembers its size between launches. AI model used is now accurately logged per transcription.</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="https://github.com/agarwalvivek29/VibeFlow/releases/tag/v1.2" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="changelog-link">Full release notes &rarr;</a>
