      <div class="changelog-entry">
        <div class="changelog-meta">
          <span class="changelog-version">v1.1.0</span>
          <span class="changelog-date">Mar 28, 2026</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="changelog-title">Memory &amp; Reliability</h3>
        <ul class="changelog-items">
          <li><strong>Critical Memory Fix</strong> &mdash; Eliminated a staircase memory leak (400 MB → 4+ GB) caused by 7 reactive observers rebuilding models on every keystroke. Models now only rebuild on Save Settings.</li>
          <li><strong>Model Load Error Surfacing</strong> &mdash; If WhisperKit or the local SLM fails to load, a red banner with Retry / Change Model appears on the Dashboard. Recording is blocked until the model is healthy.</li>
          <li><strong>HUD Processing State</strong> &mdash; Spinner + "Processing…" shown after release while transcription + AI cleanup runs. A red error pill appears for 3 s on failure.</li>
          <li><strong>Settings Save UX</strong> &mdash; All changes are held locally until you press Save Settings. Navigating away with unsaved changes shows a discard confirmation.</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="https://github.com/agarwalvivek29/VibeFlow/releases/tag/v1.1.0" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="changelog-link">Full release notes &rarr;</a>
